name: FAKE NEWZ
description:
This is from a song I wrote and produced called "FAKE NEWZ" inspired by the rapid spread of misinformation at the beginning of the Covid-19 pandemic. The whole world was in a panic and social media had all sorts of theories flying around. It was now mentally taxing to be online and that inspired me to write this. Its dedicated to anyone who felt the same way and still does because now the narrative as progressed to the vaccine. This song isnt pro or against the vaccine what I do stand against is misinformation.

This is a 1 0f 1 1920 x 1080 Visualiser
